#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:4
msgid "Using Constraints in Animation"
msgstr "在动画中使用约束"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:6
msgid ""
":doc:`Constraints </rigging/constraints/index>` are a way to control an "
"object's properties (its location/rotation/scale), using either plain "
"static values (like the :doc:`\"limit\" ones "
"</rigging/constraints/transform/limit_location>`), or (an)other "
"object(s), called \"targets\" (like e.g. the :doc:`\"copy\" ones "
"</rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location>`)."
msgstr ""
"：DOC：`约束</rigging/constraints/index> "
"'是一种将控制对象的属性（其位置/旋转/缩放），无论是使用普通的静态值（如：文档：`“限制”的人</rigging/constraints/transform/limit_location>"
" "
"`），或（一）其他物体上，所谓的“目标”（如如：文档：`“拷贝”的人</rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location>"
" `）。"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:12
msgid ""
"Even though these constraints might be useful in static projects, their "
"main usage is obviously in animation. There are two different aspects in "
"constraints' animation:"
msgstr "虽然这些限制可能是静态的项目中非常有用，它们的主要用途是明显的动画。有在约束“动画两个不同的方面："

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:16
msgid ""
"You can control an object's animation through the targets used by its "
"constraints (this is a form of indirect animation)."
msgstr "可以通过使用其约束目标控制对象的动画（这是间接的动画的形式）。"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:18
msgid "You can animate constraints' settings"
msgstr "你可以使用如下设置来调整运动效果："

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:22
msgid "Controlling Animation with Constraints"
msgstr "使用约束来控制动画"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:24
msgid ""
"This applies only to constraints using target(s). Indeed, these targets "
"can then control the constraint's owner's properties, and hence, "
"animating the targets will indirectly animate the owner."
msgstr "这仅适用于使用目标（S）的约束。事实上，这些目标就可以控制约束的所有者的特性，因此，动画的目标将间接动画的所有者。"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:28
msgid ""
"This indirect \"constraint\" animation can be very simple, like for "
"example with the :doc:`Copy Location constraint "
"</rigging/constraints/transform/copy_location>`, where the owner object "
"will simply copy the location of its target (with an optional constant "
"offset). But you can also have very complex behaviors, like when using "
"the :doc:`Action constraint </rigging/constraints/relationship/action>`, "
"which is a sort of :doc:`Animation Driver </animation/drivers>` for "
"actions!"
msgstr ""
"这间接的\"约束\"动画可以非常简单，像为例: doc: 副本位置约束，在那里所有者对象将简单地复制其目标 (与恒定的可选偏移量) "
"的位置。但你也可以有非常复杂的行为，这样，在使用时: doc: '行动约束'，这是一种的: doc:' 动画驱动程序 ' 行动!"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:35
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We should also mention the classical :doc:`Child of Constraint "
"</rigging/constraints/relationship/child_of>`, which creates parent/child"
" relationship. These relationships indeed imply indirect animation (as "
"transforming the parent affects by default all its children). But the "
"*Child Of* constraint is also very important, as it allows you to parent "
"your objects to bones, and hence use :doc:`Armatures "
"</rigging/armatures/index>` to animate them!"
msgstr ""
"我们还应提到古典: doc: '的孩子 ' 约束，该约束创建父/子关系。这些关系的确意味着间接动画 (作为转换父影响默认情况下它的孩子)。但 * "
"的孩子 * 约束也是非常重要的因为它允许你父到骨头，你对象，因此使用: doc: '电枢' 进行动画处理他们!"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:41
msgid ""
"Back to our simple *Copy Location* example, you can have two different "
"behaviors of this constraint:"
msgstr "回到我们简单 * 副本位置 * 示例中，您可以有两种不同行为的此约束:"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:44
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When it's *Offset* button is disabled (the default), the location of the "
"owner is \"absolutely\" controlled by the constraint's target, which "
"means nothing (except other constraints below in the stack...) will be "
"able to control the owner's position. Not even the object's animation "
"curves."
msgstr ""
"当其 * 偏移量 * 按钮将被禁用 (默认值)，所有者的位置是\"绝对\"受约束的目标，这意味着什么 (除了下面...堆栈中其他约束) "
"将能够控制主人的位置。即使对象的动画曲线。"

#: ../../manual/animation/constraints.rst:47
msgid ""
"However, when the *Offset* button is enabled, the location of the owner "
"is \"relatively\" controlled by the constraint's target. This means that "
"location's properties of the owner are offset from the location of the "
"target. And these owner's location properties can be controlled e.g. by "
"its *Loc...* curves (or actions, or NLA...)!"
msgstr ""
"然而，当 * 偏移量 * "
"按钮处于启用状态，所有者的位置\"相对\"受约束的目标。这意味着所有者的位置的属性的垂距目标的位置。这些所有者的位置属性可以通过例如控制其 * "
"井场。* 曲线 (或行动或 NLA...)!"

